Let me analyze the target image and provide the solution:

Analysis of Main Target Image:
- The image shows two structures side by side
- Left structure: 3 blocks (2 green vertical blocks sandwiched between 2 yellow horizontal blocks)
- Right structure: 6 blocks (From bottom: yellow horizontal, red+orange vertical pair, green+blue vertical pair, yellow horizontal on top)
- Both structures have 3 layers vertically

Block Identification:
For Left Structure:
- Bottom: Yellow horizontal block (index 11)
- Middle: Two green vertical blocks (index 7)
- Top: Yellow horizontal block (index 11)

For Right Structure:
- Bottom: Yellow horizontal block (index 11)
- Middle layer left: Red cube (index 4)
- Middle layer right: Orange cube (index 3)
- Upper layer left: Green cube (index 2)
- Upper layer right: Blue cube (index 1)
- Top: Yellow horizontal block (index 11)

Assembly Instructions:
{
    Step1: Move block with index 11 (bottom yellow horizontal)
    Step2: Move block with index 7 (left green vertical)
    Step3: Move block with index 7 (right green vertical)
    Step4: Move block with index 11 (top yellow horizontal)
    Step5: Move block with index 11 (bottom yellow horizontal for right structure)
    Step6: Move block with index 4 (red cube)
    Step7: Move block with index 3 (orange cube)
    Step8: Move block with index 2 (green cube)
    Step9: Move block with index 1 (blue cube)
    Step10: Move block with index 11 (top yellow horizontal)
}
